node.text: We sat down to talk all about her music career for my #OnThatNote series but we talked about everything from music, family, & some of her toughest times! This really felt like it was her time to #SpeakOnIt! Make sure to go to #KandiOnline & turn on your notifications. Believe me you don’t want to miss this interview!

My girl @sewjodie sat down with me to #SpeakOnIT! She talked all about the different procedures she’s done #panniculectomy #gastricsleeve #tummytuck #lipo #breastlift & she shared her experience of why she prefers to go to the #DominicanRepublic for body work. Also her & her partner @bella_bell26 just opened their own recovery house there, @bellachristinarh. 
It was so much good info in this one! Check it out on my Youtube #KandiOnline.
